{"tid":2141048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[1人1信] 要求記協對「便衣」稱呼作出更正","createTime":"2020-08-05T11:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:06:57.000Z","uid":272569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abf8de0e2f0f55d1b9a4b7d372a9a4ff7e1bae65","tid":2141048,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"見到好多報道都對示威現場某種生物以「便衣」「便衣警員」稱呼，但對其他事件則用「劫匪」「賊人」攪到市民好混亂。<br />\n<br />\n好似早排搶金鋪同大圍斬人事件，啲裝束及武器與便衣警員一樣，但報道又用「賊人」稱呼，極混亂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjhWa26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjhWa26.jpg&h=214f664c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4B4jWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4B4jWF.jpg&h=00817415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外根據公開資料警察通例講明<em><span class=\"small\">便衣人員不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">行使警察權力時，必須表明身分<strong><span class=\"red\">及</span></strong>出示委任證</span></span>。</span></em>，但現場某生物雖然衣着及武器似便衣警員，而且<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">均未能出示委任證</span></span>，但報道反而用左「便衣」。<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家一人一信要求記協出更正，唔好誤導香港人，導致香港人變得冷血唔出手救人。要求更正為「疑似冒警」「武裝分子」稱呼，對任何穿著相似警察制服人士，包括口罩面罩反光貼都不應該用「警察」「防暴」等稱呼。<br />\n<br />\n記者協會<br />\n如有任何查詢，歡迎聯絡本會。<br />\n地址 : 香港灣仔駱克道348-350 號 恒發商業大廈15樓A座<br />\n電話 : (852) 2591 0692<br />\n傳真 : (852) 2572 7329<br />\n電郵 : hkja@hkja.org.hk<br />\nFacebook :<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKJA.official%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F2%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=b6798383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/</a><br />\nTwitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKJA_OFFICIAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKJA_OFFICIAL&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F2%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=1ef8864d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKJA_OFFICIAL</a>"},{"pid":"097bc22e218637244ffebf15918f7d2a50e7c9d8","tid":2141048,"uid":65063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"贊成 太混亂啦"},{"pid":"056856315df668db0917493af94a5fa7a8b61e7f","tid":2141048,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:58:14.000Z","msg":"好混亂"},{"pid":"4a3e45c06a56f4cb004be2a5e92222516f7581cd","tid":2141048,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"我第一日已經叫大家咪再叫佢地便衣"}]}